flowchart LR
    subgraph controlPlane [控制平面]
        API[API服务]
        Orchestrator[编排引擎]
        Scheduler2[调度器]
        MetaDB2[(元数据库)]
    end

    subgraph dataPlane2 [数据平面]
        Source[(源库)]
        Target[(目标库)]
        Engines[执行引擎]
    end

    API --> Orchestrator
    Orchestrator --> Scheduler2
    Orchestrator --> MetaDB2
    Scheduler2 --> Engines
    Engines --> Source
    Engines --> Target
